StartupLab Winter Pitch Party

17 January 2020

There is no better way to start off the year than celebrating StartupLab's 5th annual Winter Pitch Party. It's hands down one of the best events in the scene, and is always something to look forward to.

The format of the event is fairly standard, albeit surprisingly casual, with 24 fire pitches from nervous entrepeneurs in all sorts of fields, followed by alcohol infused "mingeling", or networking, or whatver it's called.
